title: Nick Jonas Set to Join Demi Lovato's Tour Instead of Adam Lambert
text: Demi Lovato is changing up her tour lineup, according to TMZ. The 23-year-old singer and actress was scheduled to have Adam Lambert join her when she hit the road to support her album “Confident” but it sounds like Nick Jonas will be opening instead.
